The paper discusses the process of refactoring legacy applications to Microservices architecture, which falls under the software engineering (cs.SE) category. The paper also discusses decomposition techniques, which is related to software design (cs.SD) and distributed computing (cs.DC). The paper also mentions tool support, which is related to programming languages (cs.PL) and deep learning (cs.DL) for automated refactoring.
